            <description>Crossing: 523793Y&lt;br&gt;Road Name: ERIE STREET in WILLOUGHBY, OH, LAKE County&lt;br&gt;Crossing Closed?: No&lt;br&gt;Railroad: CSX&lt;br&gt;Division: GREAT LAKES, MP: QD-163.65&lt;br&gt;Last Update: 12/28/2022 0:00&lt;br&gt;Google Maps: https://maps.google.com/?t=k&amp;q=41.6465849,-81.4064411&lt;br&gt;Street View: https://maps.google.com/?t=k&amp;layer=c&amp;cbll=41.6465849,-81.4064411&lt;br&gt;Railroad Speed: 70.0&lt;br&gt;Railroad Traffic: 19.0&lt;br&gt;Road LRSID: nan&lt;br&gt;Road Speed: 25.0&lt;br&gt;Road AADT: 8799.0&lt;br&gt;AADT Year: 2011.0&lt;br&gt;Road Speed: 25.0&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Number of Fatalities/Injuries:&lt;br&gt;Uninjured: 4&lt;br&gt;Injured: 3&lt;br&gt;Killed: 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Incident 1&lt;br&gt;Incident Description: &lt;br&gt;I00904 WAS TRAVELING WEST ON #1 MAIN TRACK AT ERIE STREET CROSSING STRUCK A TOYOTA  SUV THAT WAS CROSSING AROUND GATES.. PROTECTION ALSO AT CROSSING: ADVANCE WARNING AND PAVEMENT MARKINGS ( RR XING SYMBOLS)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Date (Y/M/D):&lt;br&gt;2022/09/05&lt;br&gt;State: Ohio&lt;br&gt;Xing Name: 523793Y&lt;br&gt;The following values were translated from their original records;&lt;br&gt;Vehicle Type: other motor veh.&lt;br&gt;Train Direction: east&lt;br&gt;Railroad Equipment: Train (units pulling)&lt;br&gt;Accident Circumstances: Rail equipment struck highway user&lt;br&gt;Entity Transporting Hazard: Neither&lt;br&gt;Visibility: dusk&lt;br&gt;Weather: Cloudy&lt;br&gt;Type of Consist: Freight train&lt;br&gt;Type of Track: main&lt;br&gt;Train Speed Type: Estimated&lt;br&gt;Location of Warning: both sides&lt;br&gt;Crossing Warnings Connected with Highway: No&lt;br&gt;Lights at Crossing: Yes&lt;br&gt;Motorist Passed Standing Hwy Vehicle: No&lt;br&gt;Motorist Struck by Second Train: No&lt;br&gt;Motorist Action: Drove around or thru the gate&lt;br&gt;Primary Obstruction of Track View: not obstructed&lt;br&gt;Highway Driver Casualty: uninjured&lt;br&gt;Highway Driver in Vehicle: yes&lt;br&gt;