            <name>509454K</name>
            <description>Crossing: 509454K&lt;br&gt;Road Name: WENTZ ROAD in TOLEDO, OH, LUCAS County&lt;br&gt;Crossing Closed?: No&lt;br&gt;Railroad: NS&lt;br&gt;Division: GREAT LAKES, MP: CD-293.8&lt;br&gt;Last Update: 5/1/2022 0:00&lt;br&gt;Google Maps: https://maps.google.com/?t=k&amp;q=41.6279707,-83.6452979&lt;br&gt;Street View: https://maps.google.com/?t=k&amp;layer=c&amp;cbll=41.6279707,-83.6452979&lt;br&gt;Railroad Speed: 79.0&lt;br&gt;Railroad Traffic: 51.0&lt;br&gt;Road LRSID: nan&lt;br&gt;Road Speed: nan&lt;br&gt;Road AADT: 3632.0&lt;br&gt;AADT Year: 2008.0&lt;br&gt;Road Speed: nan&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Number of Fatalities/Injuries:&lt;br&gt;Uninjured: 4&lt;br&gt;Killed: 2&lt;br&gt;Injured: 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Incident 1&lt;br&gt;Incident Description: &lt;br&gt;GRADE CROSSING: TRAIN 48/448(19) OPERATING WITH ENGINE 104, ENGINE 123 AND 11 CARS, PLACED THE TRAIN INTO EMERGENCY DUE TO STRIKING AN UNOCCUPIED VEHICLE AT WENZ RD (DOT509454K)/MP RD293.8. THE OCCUPANTS OF THE VEHICLE EXITED THE VEHICLE PRIOR TO IT BEHIND STRUCK. THERE WAS MINOR DAMAGE TO THE ENGINEER SIDE OF THE PLOW ON LEAD ENGINE 104.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Date (Y/M/D):&lt;br&gt;2022/07/20&lt;br&gt;State: Ohio&lt;br&gt;Xing Name: 509454K&lt;br&gt;The following values were translated from their original records;&lt;br&gt;Vehicle Type: van&lt;br&gt;Train Direction: east&lt;br&gt;Railroad Equipment: Train (units pulling)&lt;br&gt;Accident Circumstances: Rail equipment struck highway user&lt;br&gt;Entity Transporting Hazard: Neither&lt;br&gt;Visibility: dark&lt;br&gt;Weather: Clear&lt;br&gt;Type of Consist: Passenger train&lt;br&gt;Type of Track: main&lt;br&gt;Train Speed Type: Estimated&lt;br&gt;Location of Warning: both sides&lt;br&gt;Crossing Warnings Connected with Highway: No&lt;br&gt;Lights at Crossing: Yes&lt;br&gt;Motorist Passed Standing Hwy Vehicle: Unknown&lt;br&gt;Motorist Struck by Second Train: No&lt;br&gt;Motorist Action: Stopped on crossing&lt;br&gt;Primary Obstruction of Track View: n